<br>
I still think it is funny when people complain about our pets, I solo all the time for exp with em. with a /stand, cast bezerker, sit hot button you can watch tv while these guys take mobs down.  when I am on lower dark blues I even pull with slow, I get hit very hard once hehe and then it is stand cast sit from that point on. all this whacking is great for my dodge skills I am sure. Oh and on nastys that seem like they might have a chance to win?  chain color and see if you cant take down very tough mobs with only half mana.<br>
